T02D3749:84b-4: 'phags pa dzambha la la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3749:84b-5: dpal ldan chu dbang mgon po ni //
T02D3749:84b-6: zhal gcig phyag gnyis brjed pa'i sku //
T02D3749:84b-8: mi bskyod sangs rgyas dbu la bzhugs //
T02D3749:84b-9: klu chen brgyad kyi rgyan gyis brgyan //
T02D3749:84b-11: phyag g-yas thod pa khrag bkang bsnams //
T02D3749:84b-12: g-yon pa gter gyi ne'u le 'dzin //
T02D3749:84b-13: 'gro ba dbul bas rab gdungs pa'i //
T02D3749:84b-15: khro bo'i cha lugs dbu skra gyen du brje sa
T02D3749:84b-16: // mi'u thung byis ba gzhon pa'i sha rgyas pa
T02D3749:84b-17: // nor bdag gdan la brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
T02D3749:84b-18: dgos 'dod ma lus 'byung la phyag 'tshal ba stod //
T02D3749:84b-19: mche ba rab gtsigs h'um sgras ma rungs gdul //
T02D3749:84b-20: dran pa tsam gyis ci bsams 'grub par mdzad //
T02D3749:84b-21: yid bzhin nor bu yon tan kun ldan pa //
T02D3749:84b-22: dpal ldan chu dbang khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D3749:84b-23: au tsushma la gus pas bstod pa yis //
T02D3749:84b-24: bsod nams mtha' yas dam pa gang thob des //
T02D3749:84b-25: bdag dang sems can ma lus thams cad kyi //
T02D3749:84b-26: dbul phongs sdug bsngal 'ching las grol bar shog /'phags
T02D3749:84b-27: pa rmugs 'dzin la bstod pa pandi ta dzny'a na
